{"id": 3047, "genre": 1000, "title": "这年头你在生活中都碰到过哪些“兼容难题”？", "description": "同一件事放在不同的终端/载体上，感觉……总是有点不太一样。（题图来自：iStock ©️ candy）", "record_count": 4632, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191103015739oC20pYxG1tPlLnNK.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-02T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6012, "title": "这年头你在生活中都碰到过哪些“兼容难题”？", "content": "这年头你在生活中都碰到过哪些“兼容难题”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349106, "content": "纸质书上的文字，放到屏幕上就没有耐心看完", "image": "img/option/option/20191103015835Coy8clS9Vm1A2Pp5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349107, "content": "Word 里敲好的文章，必须打印出来看才能找到问题", "image": "img/option/option/201911030200480LBDAWb6vqNREegU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349108, "content": "语音转成文字之后，读起来总会觉得有点奇怪", "image": "img/option/option/20191103020158EJrMT2puHKNRG43t.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349109, "content": "电脑上的长文章，放到手机里就读不进去", "image": "img/option/option/20191103020226aDeBJ5XZ1qQwvgbY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349110, "content": "都是记笔记，总觉得纸笔好像比手机备忘录更好使", "image": "img/option/option/20191103020343r3RZV109M5YEaDkF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349111, "content": "线上熟练使用的流行语，放到线下说就觉得很尬", "image": "img/option/option/20191103021139uGVNJn8DYMfgeBUI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349112, "content": "同一部电影，线上看似乎不如在影院容易进入气氛", "image": "img/option/option/20191103020554MBqCfkTnRiNY4Klg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349113, "content": "现金支付，会比用手机支付更有花钱的郑重感", "image": "img/option/option/20191103021036Rsxa9PV3gCtZycIe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349114, "content": "还好，我各种状态都能兼容/我遇到了其他难题", "image": "img/option/option/201911030219334XvmA6rcy9TLhGY1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}